{"tid":1401633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，狗開槍之反制","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:06:21.000Z","uid":218298,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"635c6b135eee97ed5b070d8d5cfffb5f4b4855e0","tid":1401633,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！成日都有班無委任證既狗開槍，真係世界大亂。<br />\n<br />\n而我而家就話比你地聽，要反制開槍既方法 就係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">離開現場</span><br />\n<br />\n千萬唔好係班狗範圍內大量投擲裝滿麵粉既扭蛋，呢個行為係非常危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉塵燃燒（英語：Dust explosion）指懸浮在封閉或侷限空間中，或戶外環境的可燃粉塵顆粒快速燃燒，如果在封閉環境中，可燃顆粒或侷限在大氣或是氧分子等其他合適的氣體介質中分散濃度足夠高，粉塵爆炸就有可能出現。<br />\n<br />\n粉塵爆炸常被特效藝術家、電影工作者和煙火設計師使用。<br />\n<br />\nSource:維基百科<br />\n<br />\n不開槍 不走火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03785235691a8dd0aac92a705c25a03f9527049a","tid":1401633,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e656fddc493411df85eed1d9fade189d1b0316f","tid":1401633,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"578f1d0bceb711398e88ca9e00395ccf5ee9d473","tid":1401633,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"你老母 離開現場啊<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e0e5821ce209c9e975138b0ec393b3f9d9124e","tid":1401633,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"請大家離開危險地方 多謝合作<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f693cf0831f438e59c640aa9befeb984f720a56","tid":1401633,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎美帝在港設中程導彈 HKers welcome the US to deploy a missile in&nbsp;HK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/